name: acromantula
description: Unless you have Hagrid’s opinion, Acromantula are one of the less friendly inhabitants of the Forbidden Forest. Hagrid, you really need to pick better friends. According to the Fantastic Beasts and Where to Find Them textbook, the Acromantula is a ‘monstrous eight-eyed spider capable of human speech’. But would you really want to chat with one?
